He did his best jokes, including a warning to parents “If your kid is named Marco, don’t lose him near a swimming pool.”  He says “I won the whole thing, mainly because I was the only  fourth grader that wasn’t singing “Living La Vida Loca” or “What A Girl Wants.””  At that moment, Myles committed his life to making people laugh.

Since that momentous talent show, Myles has been showcasing at, placing and winning comedy competitions all over the country. He says even though he’s busy, “I always do my best to stay in shape:  My secret, Photo Shop.”
